if I explained why I was wearing it.

00:16:26.110 --> 00:16:30.531
So I thought I would just take it
and put it back later.

00:16:32.700 --> 00:16:35.369
-Let me take you to the hospital.
-No, I'm okay.

00:16:39.248 --> 00:16:40.499
I'm really okay.

00:16:40.582 --> 00:16:43.502
This happens every now and then.

00:16:44.294 --> 00:16:46.839
The doctor said it's okay too.

00:16:46.922 --> 00:16:47.965
It's called

00:16:48.507 --> 00:16:51.927
vasovagal something.

00:16:52.011 --> 00:16:55.848
It sounds like a serious illness,
but it's just fainting.

00:16:59.101 --> 00:17:00.310
Are you sure you're okay?

00:17:01.729 --> 00:17:03.272
