00:19:36.925 --> 00:19:40.596
Why should I lie just to help you?

00:19:42.681 --> 00:19:45.058
I'll do anything I can
to return your favor.

00:19:45.142 --> 00:19:46.810
How?

00:19:46.894 --> 00:19:47.936
With money?

00:19:48.645 --> 00:19:49.646
Do you have money?

00:19:51.231 --> 00:19:54.151
